Subject: Issue with Recent Order #78910

Dear Customer Support Team,

I hope this email finds you well. I am writing regarding my recent order (#78910) placed on your website. Unfortunately, I have encountered an issue with the delivery. The tracking information shows that the package was marked as delivered, but I have not received it. I’ve checked with my neighbors and the local post office, but they don’t have any record of it. Could you please investigate this matter and provide an update? I’ve attached the order confirmation and shipping details for your reference.

Additionally, I would appreciate it if you could confirm whether a replacement or refund is possible in case the package is lost. Thank you for your assistance, and I look forward to your prompt response.

Best regards,

Hello Support,

I’ve been using your mobile app for several months without issues, but after the latest update (v3.2.0), it crashes immediately upon launch. I’ve tried reinstalling, clearing cache, and restarting my device (iPhone 14, iOS 16.5), but the problem persists. This is affecting my ability to access important account features.

Could you please escalate this to your technical team? If there’s a known issue, is there an estimated fix timeline? Alternatively, are there any workarounds, such as rolling back to a previous version? I’ve attached a screen recording of the crash for reference.
